description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'HIIT Indoor Cycling Workout | 30 Minute Intervals: Fitness Training' from the channel Global Cycling Network.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Subscribe to GCN Training: https://gcn.eu/GCNTraining

James leads another 30 minute cycling workout, which will get you fit fast. This interval session is perfect for burning fat and building your 30 second max effort. Make sure you warm up properly, have enough water to drink and get sprinting. You can use a road bike on a turbo trainer, on the rollers or an indoor bike.
